title: Prince of Persia: The Lost Crown GameSpot Review
description: Prince of Persia boldly reinvents itself as a metroidvania, and it feels like it has found its new home.

title: 15 Biggest Horror Games Coming Out in 2024 and Beyond
description: With games like the Dead Space Remake, Resident Evil 4 Remake, and Alan Wake 2, 2023 was an incredible horror. It creates the question: After such an incredible year, what can 2024 bring? Well - here are the 15 Biggest Horror Games Coming Out in 2024 and Beyond.
